data.description:
2021 summary 
Installed Nest thermostat, smart light switches (Wemo) compatible with multiple applications, Wireless Light Bulbs with Bluetooth Philips Hue White and Color, custom barn doors, 8x10ft shed, stained privacy wood fence, installed towel rings, Magnifying Mirror (master and guest bathroom), camera doorbell, cabinet handles (kitchen and bathrooms), garage door weather strip, in-wall cable kit (2nd fl foyer and living room) for mounting tv, 200lb capacity garage shelving, and laundry room wire shelving. Installed in-Wall Cable Concealer Kit in foyer and living room. 

Added rubber mulch to perimeter of house, soil and grass, smart refrigerator, washer and dryer, epoxy garage floor, and painted garage walls.

2022 summary 
Installed garage flood lights, Under Sink Drinking Water Filtration System, smart ceiling fans (3 out of 4 bed rooms, and living room), garage and front entrance wall coat rack, and barn door hidden closet under stairs.
